<div class="title">More Addictive Than Heroin</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines - Adderall</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=AD%231fan&Exact=1">AD#1fan</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; AD#1fan. "More Addictive Than Heroin: An Experience with Amphetamines - Adderall (exp30224)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 12, 2007. erowid.org/exp/30224</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
